About the app
-------------
	A simple todo app built using dmenu (suckless.org).

Usage
-----
	todo [-f]
		-f - Folder to save the todo tasks


Features
--------
	* List tasks for a day	
	* Add tasks
	* Delete tasks
		
ToDo
